properties.Name: RelatedPartyAuthenticationMethod
properties.Description: A method that can be used to authenticate a related party with a particular relationship to the party. Note that not all identification, security questions or biometrics may be considered suitable or sufficient for related party authentication.

Columns.Name: RelatedPartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.

Columns.Name: RelatedPartyAuthenticationMethodId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Related Party Authentication Method.

Columns.Name: RelatedPartyAuthenticationMethodPeriodStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period start timestamp that the related party is associated with the authentication method.

Columns.Name: RelatedPartyAuthenticationMethodPeriodEndTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period end timestamp that the related party is associated with the authentication method.

Columns.Name: AuthenticationMethodId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Authentication Method.

Columns.Name: RelatedPartyAuthenticationMethodNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the related party authentication method.

Columns.Name: PartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.

Columns.Name: SecurityQuestionNumber
Columns.Description: The number associated with the order in which the question is asked for the purpose of identification.

Columns.Name: IdentificationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the identification.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period start timestamp that the party is associated with the security question.

Columns.Name: BiometricTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a biometric type.

Columns.Name: Timestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp that the associated information is reported, recorded or effective as-of.
